# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:11
translate french rebaq4_d44c5f4d:

    # rb "Do you believe in God?"
    rb "Tu crois en Dieu ?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:15
translate french rebaq4_d250364f:

    # rb "I do too."
    rb "Moi aussi."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:16
translate french rebaq4_39e39dbc:

    # rb "I'm not sure I believe everything in the Bible. Some of that stuff is crazy."
    rb "Je ne suis pas sûr de croire à tout ce qui est écrit dans la Bible. Certaines choses sont complètement dingues."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:17
translate french rebaq4_fca32428:

    # rb "But I do believe in God."
    rb "Mais je crois en Dieu."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:19
translate french rebaq4_000451d3:

    # rb "I just wonder if He's still around sometimes."
    rb "Je me demande juste parfois s’Il est toujours là."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:20
translate french rebaq4_beacf1f7:

    # rb "It almost seems like He gave up on us a long time ago."
    rb "On dirait presque qu’Il nous a abandonnés il y a longtemps."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:23
translate french rebaq4_fd33eaf2:

    # rb "I get that. I believe in God, but sometimes it's hard to see Him."
    rb "Je comprends ça. Je crois en Dieu, mais parfois, c’est dur de Le voir."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:24
translate french rebaq4_bf454912:

    # rb "Sometimes it seems like He gave up on us a long time ago."
    rb "Parfois, on dirait qu’Il nous a abandonnés il y a longtemps."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:26
translate french rebaq4_c4ccd1ac:

    # rb "That's okay."
    rb "Ce n’est pas grave."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:27
translate french rebaq4_ec2bb09f:

    # rb "I do believe in God, but I'm not going to judge you if you don't."
    rb "Je crois en Dieu, mais je ne vais pas te juger si tu n’y crois pas."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:29
translate french rebaq4_d92a9b75:

    # rb "It seems like the more a person sees and understands about the world, the harder it is to believe in God."
    rb "On dirait que plus on voit et comprend le monde, plus il est difficile de croire en Dieu."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:30
translate french rebaq4_4c048d1e:

    # rb "Even though I believe He is real, I do wonder if He still cares about us, or if He gave up on us a long time ago."
    rb "Même si je crois qu’Il existe, je me demande s’Il se soucie encore de nous, ou s’Il nous a abandonnés il y a longtemps."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:32
translate french rebaq4_658f1a22:

    # rb "Or maybe there's just so many people in the world now that He has a hard time paying attention to all of us at once."
    rb "Ou peut-être qu’il y a simplement tellement de gens dans le monde aujourd’hui qu’Il a du mal à s’occuper de nous tous en même temps."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:34
translate french rebaq4_d92ec1a7:

    # rb "Maybe that's why the world seems to be getting worse and worse."
    rb "C’est peut-être pour ça que le monde semble aller de plus en plus mal."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:35
translate french rebaq4_551eda30:

    # pc "It's not all bad though."
    pc "Mais tout n’est pas noir pour autant."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:37
translate french rebaq4_b54a2fcf:

    # rb "No, you're right. Good things happen too. Like me finding you."
    rb "Non, tu as raison. Il y a aussi de bonnes choses. Comme le fait que je t’aie trouvé."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:39
translate french rebaq4_9c82a3e0:

    # rb "Maybe that was God turning my direction for once."
    rb "Peut-être que c’était Dieu qui, pour une fois, a orienté mes pas vers toi."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq4.rpy:41
translate french rebaq4_3f2e551a:

    # rb "I guess there are a lot of other people out there who need His help more than I do."
    rb "J’imagine qu’il y a beaucoup d’autres personnes qui ont davantage besoin de Son aide que moi."

